summary: Norio Sakuragi, Ayame’s father and a rather well known shield agent that taught at the operations academy for a while. He...
body:
Norio Sakuragi, Ayame’s father and a rather well known shield agent that taught at the operations academy for a while. He commonly went on missions alongside Yvena and his specialty was either stealth or close combat. He was also one of the most common disciplinary officers at the academy.

As a kitsune he’s lived for quite a while, and decided to leave his clan due to a disagreement over humanity,this has led him to watch over the growth and evolution of society, which eventually led him into joining shield.
